snippet.title: Student Web Series || Episode - 7 || Shanmukh Jaswanth || Subbu K || Infinitum Media
snippet.description:
To all the students out there!!!!!!!
Here's the most related tale that'll make you laugh and cry at the same time. Episode 7 is out now.

Disclaimer: We do not intend to promote investment/gambling of any kind.  Viewer discretion is advised. If your current residence is from Andhra, Assam, Odisha, Telangana, Nagaland, and Sikkim, you are advised to not participate.
 
For Brand Inquiries & Collaborations 
Email us at brands@infinitumnetwork.in

"Student" is Telugu's biggest and most ambitious web series featuring Shanmukh Jaswanth as a lead.

Cast: Shanmukh Jaswanth, Don Pruthvi, Pruthvi Jhakaas, Neha Pathan, Tanuja Madhurapantula, Tejaswini Naidu, Sathwik Somalanka, Naga Vedith, Devesh, Vijay Arun Cr, Pranaya Vamsi, Madhu Nekkalapudi, Pranaya Vamsy Rambhatla(PVR).

Produced by Infinitum​ Network Solutions.
Co-Producer: Shanmukh Jaswanth

Written by  Subbu. K 

Directed by Avinash 

Cinematography: Vamsi Srinivas 

Music: Anivee
Additional programming - Ashok Sridharan
Flute - Sanjay Balajee

snippet.title: FilterCopy | Falling In Love After Arranged Marriage | Ft. Anshuman Malhotra,  Esha Kansara
snippet.description:
From arranged marriage to happily ever after, we found love ❤️

Approximately 12 million in India are living with epilepsy* - a neurological condition. It is surrounded by social stigma and taboos that emanate due to lack of correct information. 

Sanofi (India) wants to change that!

This film helps bust many common myths about epilepsy, so the right information can help spread awareness. Watch it to rid yourself of any misconceptions about epilepsy!  Like and share it with your network, so you help educate others, too. 

This can be your pledge to spread the word about what's right. 
To know more on epilepsy and how it can be managed, visit: http://surl.sanofi.com/daretoknowepilepsy

*Reference - Epilepsy in India I: Epidemiology and public health - PMC (nih.gov), available at https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4564458/

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3931 | 17 Nov 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3931: Jethalal Gets Impatient
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha urgently phones all of Sundar's phone numbers, but he is never able to contact him. Jetha is relieved when an uncle who is Daya's neighbor answers the phone. Jetha asks the elderly guy to connect him with Daya. The old guy pays a visit to Daya's home, but he informs Jetha that she is not there. Sundar even ignores Tapu's call. Why did Sundar not answer his phone?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3931, 17 Nov 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada

Lyrics:

Ye munasib hoga hamko thaamlo ke
Ham bhi chaand dhoondne lage hain badalon mein
Naam shamil ho chuka hai apna pagalon mein

Matlabi is duniya se kinaare karlun
Naam tere saari ki saari bahaarein kardun
Bas chale to tere hath mein sitaare rakhdun

Shaam ka rang kyon
Tere rang se mil raha hai

Dil mera tere sang
Baith kar kyon khil raha hai

Hai koi jawaab
O mere janaab
Hai koi jawaab
Is baat ka

Aapke apne hi hain hamko jaaniye to
Is sharam ke lehje ko pehchaniye to
Baat ban jayegi baat maniye to

Kya hai kuch nahi ye char din ki zindagani
Taaron ke her fer ki ye karistani
Na kabhi bhi mitne wali likh dein kahani

Aapki aankhon mein jo likha hai wo main padh raha hun

Baat wo honth par kab aayegi
Intezaar kar raha hun

Hai koi jawaab
O mere janaab
Hai koi jawaab

Bunte rahein 
Ya na bune ye khaab
Hai koi jawaab
Is baat ka
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

snippet.title: Yo Yo Honey Singh on Love, Heartbreak, Betrayal | Honey Singh Podcast | Sadhika Sehgal | MLR Ep 32
snippet.description:
Today we are in conversation with the much-awaited guest, none other than the G.O.A.T., Yo Yo Honey Singh! 

Known for laying the foundations of the OG gang, Mafia Mundeer, that gave a different hype to the Indian rap industry, Honey Singh has successfully dominated the music scene with his catchy tunes and energetic performances, on and off-screen.

As we unpack the numerous layers to his personal and professional journey in this episode with Sadhika Sehgal, we are spilling the tea on everything—from his wildest dreams to the secret sauce that keeps him at the top of the game. And yes, we're even dishing on that epic meet-up with the legend himself, AR Rahman.

From his latest songs to his upcoming documentary on Netflix, catch the ‘Angreji Beat’ fame share his thoughts on rising to fame and the fallback he experienced. 

Ever wondered what life means to Yo Yo Honey Singh? Or why do his fans adore him so much? We're getting real on all that and more—how he handles the haters, the times he's been misunderstood, and his advice for non-believers in God and the astrological realm.

We're taking you behind the scenes of his life, exploring the lessons he learned from the tough times, his fearless attitude, and, of course, the lowdown on love and heartbreak. Ishq versus pyaar, his school gang stories, thoughts on karma—you name it, we're chatting about it.

Curious about his take on male friendships and what "mardangi" (masculinity) means to him? We've got the deets. Plus, we're delving into his unconventional career advice for those who can't stand the 9-to-5 grind, and the real talk on toxic traits.

Buckle up for the ride as we spill the tea on his concert moments, including that one time he got a little heated, and yes, even his mom giving him an earful.

Don't forget to watch an exclusive peek into the life and mind of Yo Yo Honey Singh, showcasing his emotional side for the very first time on the big screen!  To know more about our Desi Kalaakar watch the full episode and get ready for all the feels!

snippet.description:
Her web connects them all. 🕸 #MadameWeb is coming soon exclusively to movie theaters.

Visit our site: https://www.madameweb.movie/

Follow Us on Social:
https://www.facebook.com/madameweb
https://www.instagram.com/madameweb
https://twitter.com/madameweb
https://www.tiktok.com/@madamewebmovie

"Meanwhile, in another universe…” In a switch from the typical genre, Madame Web tells the standalone origin story of one of Marvel publishing's most enigmatic heroines. The suspense-driven thriller stars Dakota Johnson as Cassandra Webb, a paramedic in Manhattan who may have clairvoyant abilities. Forced to confront revelations about her past, she forges a relationship with three young women destined for powerful futures...if they can all survive a deadly present.

snippet.title: Samबहादुर - Sam Ka Bahadur BTS | Vicky Kaushal | Meghna Gulzar | Ronnie S | In Cinemas 01.12.2023
snippet.description:
Feel the pulse of patriotism as Vicky Kaushal transforms into Sam Manekshaw, narrating a captivating story of dedication, honour, and unwavering courage in this exclusive BTS video.

#Samबहादुर in cinemas 1.12.2023

#SamIsHere #sambahadur 

Samबहादुर is a tribute to Field Marshal Sam HFJ Manekshaw, MC, India's first Field Marshal and a legendary Army General. His career witnessed the shaping of India's geopolitical borders, and his life was marked by significant milestones, from fighting in World War II to being the Chief of Army Staff during the 1971 Indo-Pakistan war, that led to the creation of Bangladesh.
This RSVP film explores his dynamic personality and his unparalleled military career, offering a glimpse into the life of a no-nonsense Army Commander, also known as "Sam Bahadur" by the soldiers he led.

snippet.title: Indians And Diwali | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys 
A Very Happy Diwali !!!

Special Thanks to Tanishq

As the Title is Indians And Diwali this Video has everything that happens during Diwali Festival . The most relatable and Funny Diwali Video . Scenarios like what happens on Indian families doing Diwali shopping for dhanteras shopping new utensils or jewellery shopping of gold coin , silver coin from brand like Tanishq . Kaamwali and her struggles with house cleaning waiting for diwali gifts , diwali bonus . Daughter painting diya and mom hanging diwali lights . Girls dressing up in traditional dieting whole month to look good and clicking pictures and making videos . Prepations for office diwali pooja , sisters cleaning house and competing and having fun , next day of diwali and taking off the lights , flower garlands , rangoli , giving diwali to staff , guards , kaamwali bai , Aunties for shopping for diwali pooja kheel patashe , patisha , paan , supari , sweets , favourite mathai moti choor ladoo , kaju ki barfi , bondi ke laddoo , cham cham , diwali decoration , bhandan var , diya , lights , candles , rangoli , diwali gifts dry fruits , gift box . Indian Aunties bargaining with shopkeeper , shops making huge profits during diwali dhamaka sales , going out to relatives to wish happy diwali and dealing with diwali 2023 traffic jams , giving gifts to relatives and travelling in car , indian sweets shops fully loaded with customers , eating in restaurants after diwali shopping eating dosa , chowmein , tuition mam helps kids prepare their diwali poem , diwali essay , teaching why diwali is celebrated , diwali school function costumes , diwali is the festival food , every foodie loves puri , aloo , kheer , halwa , muli ki bhujji , raita , achar , panchamrit , laxmi ganesh pooja , talking about the ban on fire crackers , diwali away from home , pg wali diwali , showing of chandi , golf gifts , buying air purifier cause of the air pollution and noise pullution caused by crackers in delhi , south delhi posh diwali partiers playing poker , drinking , tambola , diwali vlogs , diwali outfits , lehenga , suits , saree , kurti , kurta , and looking beautiful and clicking pictures . West Delhi people mocking south delhi on dieting on diwali doing keto , intermittent fasting or just drinking alchol , many more fun things covered in the diwali video .
This video is filled with Festive season memories and situations we all have been in . 
Relish and Relive your Childhood Memories of Diwali festival
Do share it with your friends and family , Relatives , Neighbour . A very happy diwali 2023 season to all of you and Happy deepawali  .. Comment down your Fav Part , 
Like , Share and 
Subscribe to our Channel - http://bit.ly/thepaayaljain | Press Bell Icon

Contact : 081302 08877

snippet.title: Door Aa Gaye (Official Video) Vishal Mishra, Dino James | VYRL Originals
snippet.description:
"Door Aa Gaye" brings together two of the most exciting musical talent together for the first time. The gifted Vishal Mishra - fresh from the success of Zihaal e Miskin & popular hip hop star Dino James - fresh out of his win from Khatron Ke Khiladi - combine forces for an unique collaboration - producing Door Aa Gaye. A lilting love track that merges the melodic vocals of Vishal and the hip-hop vibe of Dino, this one is a definite for those moody nights, when the party moves from dancing tracks to soulful soothing melodies. Door Aa Gaye is new age ode to love and longing.

#DoorAaGaye #VishalMishra #DinoJames

snippet.title: கார்த்திகை 1ஆம் நாள் | அஞ்சுமலை அழகா | Anjumalai Azhaga | ஐயப்பன் பாடல்கள் | Ayyapan Songs
snippet.description:
சிம்போனி பெருமையுடன் வழங்கும் கார்த்திகை மாதம் ஐயப்பன் பாடல்கள் 2023, தமிழ் பக்தி பாடல்கள்
பாடியவர்: புஷ்பவனம் குப்புசாமி , ஸ்ரீஹரி , உன்னி மேனன் டீ.ல்.மகாராஜன ,  உன்னிகிருஷ்ணன் 
இசை: அஜய் , கண்மணிராஜா , ஸ்ரீஹரி , கல்யாண் | ஆனந்த்  அரவிந்த் 
பாடல்கள்: அம்பிகாபதி , தேவேந்திரன் , டர்.கிருதியா , முகிலன் , செங்கதிர்வானந் , உளுந்தூர்பேட்டை ஷண்முகம், மேலநல்லூர் ஸ்ரீனிவாசன்
தயாரிப்பு மேற்பார்வை: ஸ்ரீஹரி
தயாரிப்பு: சிம்போனி ரிகார்டிங் கம்பெனி

Symphony presents Karthigai month 2023 Ayyappan songs specially selected and curated for pure Bakthi and devotion
Sung by: Pushpavanam Kuppusami, Srihari, Unni Menon, T.L.Maharajan, Unnikrishnan
Music: Ajay, Srihari, Kanmaniraja, Kalyan | Anand, Aravind
Lyrics: Ambikapathi, Devendhiran, Dr.Kiruthiya, Mugilan, Senkathirvanan, Ambikapathi, Ulundurpettai Shanmugam, Melanallur Srinivasan
Executive Producer: Srihari
Produced by Symphony Recording Co.,

The Songs included in this album can be selected by touching or clicking the timings at the beginning of that song:

0:00  Anjumalai Azhaga | அஞ்சுமலை அழகா

05:11 Manikandan Pettai Thullum | மணிகண்டன் பேட்டை துள்ளும்

11:08  Sami Gurusami | சாமி குருசாமி

15:19 Ayya Ayya Ayyappa | அய்யா அய்யா ஐயப்பா

25:38 Kanni Moola Ganapathi | கன்னிமூல கணபதி

31:59 Anandane Adhiroopane | ஆனந்தனே அதிரூபனே

38:53  Kattu kkattu | கட்டு கட்டு

42:59 Antha Ponnambalathil | அந்த பொன்னம்பலத்தில்

49:27 Pambaiyin Theeram | பம்பையின் தீரம்

பாடியவர்: புஷ்பவனம் குப்புசாமி , ஸ்ரீஹரி , உன்னி மேனன் டீ.ல்.மகாராஜன ,  உன்னிகிருஷ்ணன் 
இசை: அஜய் , கண்மணிராஜா , ஸ்ரீஹரி , கல்யாண் | ஆனந்த்  அரவிந்த்

snippet.description:
അപ്രതീക്ഷിതമായി പാറമട വീട്ടിലേക്ക് ഭവാനിയമ്മയുടെ വരവ്. ഇനി പടവലം വീട്ടിൽ നില്ക്കാൻ സാധിക്കില്ലെന്നാണ് ഭവാനിയമ്മ പറയുന്നത്. ഇനി എന്തൊക്കെ സംഭവിക്കുമെന്ന് കണ്ടറിയാം.

Bhavani amma's unexpected visit to Paramada house. She says she can't continue living in Padavalam house.  Now we will have to wait and see what happens next!

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3930 | 16 Nov 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3930: Sundar Ko Phone Lagao
--------------------------------------------------------
A customer visits the Gada Electronic Store to purchase a gift for his wife, who has been separated, and his brother-in-law keeps pushing back the date of her homecoming. Jetha connects with the customer and tells him about his brother-in-law. Jetha is eager to learn the day on which Daya will return. So he dials Sundar's number, but Sundar has thirteen phone numbers. Jetha is puzzled about which number to dial. Nattu, Kaka, and Bagha attempt to assist him. Will Jetha be able to communicate with Sundar?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3930, 16 Nov 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Best Scheme for Street Vendors | Dreamz Unlimited | Awareness
snippet.description:
The PM Street Vendor's Atmanirbhar Nidhi (PMSVANidhi) aims at facilitating
a collateral free working capital loan of upto Rs10,000 of one-yea tenure, to help street vendors resume their businesses post lockdown.
WHICH LENDING INSTITUTIONS WILL PROVIDE CREDIT?
Scheduled Commercial Banks, Regional Rural Banks, Small Finance Banks,
Co-operative Banks, Non-Banking Financial Companies,
Micro-Finance Institutions and SHG Banks.
For more details log on to;
https://pmsvanidhi.mohua.gov.in/

Diwali Mela starts in Gokuldham society. Everyone is super excited to buy festival lights, lamps, colors, and decorative items from the stalls. Bhide first inaugurates the beginning of the Mela by cutting the ribbon. Watch the full episode to know more.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonyliv #comedy #comedy2023 #jethalal #jethalalcomedy 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The residents of the housing society, help each other find solutions when they face common, real-life challenges and get involved in sticky situations.

#tmkoc #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah 

Click here to watch all the funny videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLn5vww_8o5KvbMJDIP6JtxrH5i5e8GDUE

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3929 | 15 Nov 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3929: Surprise Dham
--------------------------------------------------------
The ladies of Gokuldham have met at Anjali's house to plan their Diwali festivities. Anjali has made DIY diyas and ornamental objects out of coconut shells, which has surprised everyone. Later, everyone agreed to go to Champaklal to inquire about Daya's visit. Meanwhile, Champaklal and his childhood buddies assemble to share experiences from their youth.
